title: Digital Photography for Beginners 3rd Revised Edition - 2014  UK
description:
Digital Photography for Beginners 3rd Revised Edition - 2014  UK

196 Pages | True PDF | English | 28 MB 


Get to grips with the basic but fundamental aspects of photography, from aperture and white balance to composition and what to keep in your kit bag.  Understand how the mode dial works with in-depth guides to each of the major camera settings. From Program to Aperture, it's all covered here.  Develop your shooting skills for a range of photography styles including picture-perfect landscapes and eye-catching architecture.  Perfect your photographs even after they've been taken. Learn to fix exposure, remove red-eye, and much more.
